  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/59e309f6c05fbc219988828da4dc7d54.avif?t=1756123138\" alt=\"No pressure. No failure. No optimal path. No journey exactly the same.\" width=600 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Glitchhikers: The Spaces Between is an introspective freeform game where the player chooses from four late night journeys, slips into a liminal space, and has a unique experience travelling into their own thoughts, guided by the characters they meet along the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/703baa72f481e03ba99f47c93753a475.avif?t=1756123138\" alt=\"Meet a cast of over sixteen mysterious hikers\" width=600 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The hikers you meet on each journey will travel with you for a time, offering thought-provoking conversations, and questioning your place in the universe. Who will you meet? What will you talk about? Were they real or just a figment of your imagination?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/9c764d01f0d7df40fde2e385eb9b12c8.poster.avif?t=1756123138\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/9c764d01f0d7df40fde2e385eb9b12c8.webm?t=1756123138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/9c764d01f0d7df40fde2e385eb9b12c8.mp4?t=1756123138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/e407093b0daaf0256a7653d8cbe080d9.avif?t=1756123138\" alt=\"A space for you\" width=600 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Bask in a freeform experience that holds space for you and your thoughts – you decide on the direction, the conversations you have are always open ended, and play sessions can be as short as 30 minutes or as long as you like, with many options for replayability. Talk to passengers on a train, walk through a park with your music player, sit with your thoughts on the endless open road, or even fly through a lonely airport terminal.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/9bcbf9a12dcf56f0d95335511da6c713.poster.avif?t=1756123138\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/9bcbf9a12dcf56f0d95335511da6c713.webm?t=1756123138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/9bcbf9a12dcf56f0d95335511da6c713.mp4?t=1756123138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/3727c8d68610a12cddd89f23073ad821.avif?t=1756123138\" alt=\"More than 70 tracks accompany you through the twilight\" width=600 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover an extensive original soundtrack full of chill grooves, upbeat wonder, dreamy synths controlled by your movement through space, and that one busker who makes you feel right at home: each journey has its own feel.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/5d0b37f267132ba2ccfb03524f1ee9c0.poster.avif?t=1756123138\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/5d0b37f267132ba2ccfb03524f1ee9c0.webm?t=1756123138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/5d0b37f267132ba2ccfb03524f1ee9c0.mp4?t=1756123138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/1ce38b355ca49a816f9476a53b809b32.avif?t=1756123138\" alt=\"The full realisation of the critically acclaimed cult game\" width=600 height=151 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Expanding upon the original conceptual short game released in 2014, Glitchhikers: The Spaces Between offers returning players and newcomers even more to experience. This is a game that is here for you now, and in the future, whenever you need to find some spaces between the everyday flow of life.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/f37e1e27d87765e04a65016a8400810c.poster.avif?t=1756123138\" width=616 height=258 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/f37e1e27d87765e04a65016a8400810c.webm?t=1756123138\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/f37e1e27d87765e04a65016a8400810c.mp4?t=1756123138\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ABOUT THE DEVELOPER</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/926adabcc27e9d4cf001868204bdc485.avif?t=1756123138\" width=600 height=127 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Silverstring Media are a vital and vibrant voice within narrative indie games, creating a string of short experimental titles and working as narrative guns for hire on indie darlings including Celeste, Crypt of the Necrodancer, Where the Water Tastes Like Wine, Manifold Garden and Wandersong.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1449230/extras/6d4a462e3bce67daf73cca4d13f7554b.avif?t=1756123138\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p>",
